{"date_gmt":"2012-04-30 12:17:16", "language": "en", "author": "6645", "url": "http://laith.wordpress.com/?p=2584", "title": "Carl Froedrich Gauss [Birthday Quote]", "blog": "6638", "post_id": "508672", "tags": ["Carl Friedrich Gauss", "quote"], "blogname": "Laith&#039;s Ramblings", "date": "2012-04-30 07:17:16", "content": "<blockquote>It is not knowledge, but the act of learning, not possession but the act of getting there, which grants the greatest enjoyment.\r\n<em>les charmes enchanteux de cette sublime science ne se d\u00e9c\u00e8lent dans toute leur beaut\u00e9 qu'\u00e0 ceux qui ont le courage de l'approfondir.</em></blockquote>\r\n- <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Carl Friedrich Gauss\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carl_Friedrich_Gauss\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">Carl Friedrich Gauss</a>, <em>Scientist &amp; More,</em> born April 30th 1777", "categories": ["Quotes"], "likes": []}
