{"date_gmt":"2012-04-30 16:28:31", "language": "en", "author": "34433", "url": "http://dailyplanit.wordpress.com/?p=1536", "title": "Identify Emotions", "blog": "34442", "post_id": "94798", "tags": [], "blogname": "Daily PlanIt", "date": "2012-04-30 16:28:31", "content": "<strong>May \u2013 Emotional \u2013 Week\u00a0 One \u2013 Activity: Identify Emotions</strong>\r\n\r\nFeelings come in a wide variety of types and intensity. Learning to increase awareness to recognize the emotions we are feeling is an important skill to develop our emotional intelligence.\r\n<blockquote>This week, I will print a feelings chart and mood diary, and each evening note what I've been feeling during\u00a0 the day.</blockquote>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dotolearn.com/organizationtools/EmotionsColorWheel/index.htm\"><img class=\"wp-image-1576 alignright\" title=\"EmotionsColorWheel\" src=\"http://dailyplanit.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/emotionscolorwheel.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"423\" height=\"287\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Tools for identifying emotions</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://dailyplanitwiki.pbworks.com/w/file/FeelingsChart.pdf\">Printable Feelings Chart</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://cnvc.org/en/learn-online/feelings-list/feelings-inventory\">List of Feelings</a></li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://www.dotolearn.com/organizationtools/EmotionsColorWheel/index.htm\">Emotions Color Wheel</a></li>\r\n\t<li>Printable <a href=\"http://homepage.smc.edu/harrop_adrianne/images/Emotions.JPG\">Visual Emotions</a></li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://www.emotionalcompetency.com/recognizing.htm\">Recognizing Emotions</a> at <a href=\"http://www.emotionalcompetency.com\">www.emotionalcompentency.com</a></li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://www.getselfhelp.co.uk/docs/MoodDiary.pdf\">Printable Mood Diary</a> from <a href=\"http://www.getselfhelp.co.uk/\">http://www.getselfhelp.co.uk/</a></li>\r\n\t<li>Noticing emotions meditation <a href=\"http://www.self-compassion.org/noting.practice.MP3\">http://www.self-compassion.org/noting.practice.MP3</a></li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"http://www.helpguide.org/toolkit/developing_emotional_awareness.htm\">Developing Emotional Awareness</a> section of the <a href=\"http://www.helpguide.org/toolkit/emotional_health.htm#toolkit_homepage\">Helpguide Emotional Skills Toolkit</a></li>\r\n</ul>", "categories": ["Year of Personal Growth"], "likes": []}
