ess.\u00a0 Taxes and regulations make that impossible, and SBA money goes only to Indian and Asian Ponzi Scheme scams, no whites need apply.\r\n\r\n40 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake's hair is all gray.\r\n\r\n48 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake's son is a casualty of America's 40-year campaign in Afghanistan.\u00a0 He was unable to defend himself because Pentagon mandates left him unarmed.\r\n\r\n51 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake's 49-year old wife dies of breast cancer.\u00a0 She developed it at 41, but ObamaCare mandated that women can't get breast cancer screenings until they turn 50.\r\n\r\n57 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake watches in horror as President Obama wins his ninth term.\r\n\r\n65 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake doesn't even bother signing up for Medicare, because the brother of the former Chief of Staff for President Obama says that old white people should just die and get out of the way so that Federal money can be spent on blacks and Hispanics.\r\n\r\n67 Years Old:\u00a0 Blake dies of an ailment that a competent native born white American physician would have diagnosed, except he had nothing but H-1B legal immigrant visa holding Asian and Indian doctors with poor English skills and a fraudulently obtained medical degree.\r\n\r\nOne year after Blake's Death:\u00a0 The United States of America officially surrenders to China.", "categories": ["Uncategorized"], "likes": []}
