{"date_gmt":"2012-05-04 14:20:20", "language": "en", "author": "141553", "url": "http://countenance.wordpress.com/?p=19286", "title": "No Surprise(s)", "blog": "142127", "post_id": "11354", "tags": [], "blogname": "Countenance Blog", "date": "2012-05-04 08:20:20", "content": "A gas station in Chicago gave away free gas as part of a TV station's promotion.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://southtownstar.suntimes.com/12291303-522/free-gas-promotion-snarls-harlem-ave-in-tinley-park.html\">Guess who showed up in force.</a>\r\n\r\nI was expecting the whole thing to be a smokescreen for the CPD clearing up a bunch of warrants.\u00a0 The problem is that they'd have to arrest probably three-quarters of the people showing up for this promotion.", "categories": ["Illinois &#038; Metro East"], "likes": []}
